quired to manage the oxygen tank \n\nand/or oxygen tubing and/or provide steadying assistance/contact guard, to allow the patient to complete \nan activity safely. \n\no  Code 04, Supervision or touching assistance, if a single helper only manages the oxygen tank or the IV \n\npole and otherwise the patient needs no assistance to safely complete the activity.", "type": "Document"}}